text: Md. Shah Newaz Chowdhury is a Bangladesh Nationalist Party politician and the former Member of Parliament of Chittagong-11. ==Career== Chowdhury was elected to parliament from Chittagong-11 as a Bangladesh Nationalist Party candidate in 1991. ==References== Category:Bangladesh Nationalist Party politicians Category:Living people Category:5th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:6th Jatiya Sangsad members
title: Md. Shah Newaz Chowdhury
